{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/clip_memory.gif?t=1739781255\" /><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the shoes of <strong>Coral</strong>, one of the last survivors of a failed mission to colonize an unknown planet. Explore the wreckage of the mothership, <strong>Crystal Mountain</strong>, now a derelict vessel shrouded in flickering lights, metallic echoes, and eerie sounds. But you're not alone: alien creatures, oozing black masses with a single red eye, lurk among the ruins.</p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/clip_ghost_02.gif?t=1739781255\" /><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No explicit missions, no arrows pointing the way. Your <strong>curiosity</strong> will guide you as you freely explore and follow the hidden clues scattered throughout the game world. Piece together the traces and fragments of the past to uncover the <strong>truth</strong>. Nothing is as it seems: every discovery can reveal unexpected connections and new possibilities, unlocking <strong>secrets</strong> waiting to be found.</p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/clip_firefly.gif?t=1739781255\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Various vertically interconnected areas to explore<br></li><li> A fast-paced and dynamic combat system<br></li><li> RPG elements with unlockable abilities and upgrades<br></li><li> Free exploration: you decide what to do and where to go<br></li><li> Colossal bosses<br></li><li> Tons of secrets to discover</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123920/extras/clip_bomb_01.gif?t=1739781255\" />","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3123920?t=1739781255","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai